KSP: 0.24.2 (32bit) WIN

Problem- All but one part (the Klaw) dont show up.

EVE 7-4

ATM 3-4

Reproduction Steps- UNKNOWN

Log: http://www./?xymm6knx7imvl

Edited September 20, 2014 by kenbobo
Solved.

In the log, it looks like the Part Loader crashes while loading the LES. That's the second stock part loaded (the Klaw is the first) in a normal game, so that would explain why only the Klaw appears. Part Loader complains that it can't find the SolidFuel resource definition and then throws an NullReferenceException. I'm not sure what would cause SolidFuel to disappear, but it could be a corruption of your game files. Try reinstalling KSP or verifying the files through Steam.

No way.

Turns out my WHOLE resources thing was erased.

I was making my mod and POOF it crashed.

Fixed.
